data.description: NEW LOWER PRICE AND AN ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE IF NEEDED!!  Are you looking for the perfect first time home?  Are you considering downsizing for those retirement years?  Look no further.  We have the house!  Charming 2 BR/2BA home in a quiet neighborhood.  Picture yourself snuggled around the beautiful fireplace in your large, porcelain floored living room.  The open-concept makes it easy to entertain as you prepare for those upcoming holiday dinners while entertaining guests.  Kitchen also features porcelain floors  and solid Corian countertops.  (Kitchen island and pot hanging stand do not stay).  Hardwood flooring under the dining area and bedrooms per owner. Convenience at its finest with one floor living, although the large basement could easily be converted to an additional bedroom or rec area.  Huge wrap around porch with heavy duty firepit and covered dining area.  EXTRA LOT ACROSS THE BACK ALLEY INCLUDED -  ALMOST 1/2 ACRE(.4421 acres)  Great if you have additional cars to park or an RV.  Please call or text today to see this beautiful home.  304-670-9608
